# ğŸ“ Render With Custom Sizes

Control how much viewport width image occupies.

```liquid
{% render 'responsive-image',
  image: section.settings.image,
  sizes: '(min-width: 750px) 50vw, 100vw'
%}
```

### Common Sizes Examples

| Layout            | sizes                            |
| ----------------- | -------------------------------- |
| Full width banner | `100vw`                          |
| Two columns       | `(min-width: 750px) 50vw, 100vw` |
| 3-column grid     | `(min-width: 990px) 33vw, 100vw` |
| Product grid      | `(min-width: 1200px) 25vw, 50vw` |

